<paragraph id="C666ED6F344350E2E41D93AA24EC7002" pageId="0" pageNumber="49">
<taxonomicName id="72A676CD574EDED53287DEFF84E64924" class="Sordariomycetes" genus="Neothyronectria" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Neothyronectria citri" order="Hypocreales" pageId="0" pageNumber="49" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="citri">Neothyronectria citri</taxonomicName>
differs from its closest phylogenetic neighbour 
<taxonomicName id="BD0459CEC4840CE8FF3F1CFD7B1DFEC3" class="Sordariomycetes" genus="Neothyronectria" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Neothyronectria sophorae" order="Hypocreales" pageId="0" pageNumber="49" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="sophorae">Neothyronectria sophorae</taxonomicName>
in ITS, LSU and tub2 loci, based on the alignments deposited in TreeBASE.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
